{"tid":1472062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小小小意見","createTime":"2019-08-14T12:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:38:59.000Z","uid":12773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"044e16c0c148de0bfe26d8a4c9b6137255beafeb","tid":1472062,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:37:44.000Z","msg":"局勢愈來愈明朗<br />\n818就算五百萬人出黎遊行<br />\n港共政府同支那共產黨會答應五大訴求？<br />\n朋友，你太年輕了<br />\n又幻想用大愛去感化共產黨？<br />\n<br />\n勇武派兄弟如果隊淋幾件警犬又如何<br />\n難道港共政權又會答應五大訴求？<br />\n<br />\n現在呢場鬥爭已經變成一場真人show<br />\n絕對係一場真人show<br />\n但請謹記<br />\n睇呢場show的觀眾<br />\n唔係港共政府<br />\n唔係支那共產黨<br />\n係美英等等國家<br />\n係外國勢力<br />\n<br />\n現在唯一可以做的<br />\n是以受迫害資態<br />\n要求外國勢力支援<br />\n因為就算有五百萬人和平遊行<br />\n邪惡的共產黨亦絕對不會答應我地的任何訴求<br />\n<br />\n面對現實<br />\n歐美外國勢力<br />\n全部銀紙掛帥<br />\n送我地香港人每人一本護照<br />\n絕對係痴心妄想<br />\n可幸此時此刻正值中美貿易戰<br />\n我們必須被美歐等等國家利用<br />\n利用我們作為對支那土匪的談判籌碼<br />\n迫令港共支那答應五大訴求甚至解放香港<br />\n<br />\n所以以後每一步<br />\n請和理非繼續和理非去和平遊行去做文宣<br />\n請勇武派繼續迫警犬出醜於世界眼前<br />\n而我地的姿態<br />\n必須係被暴政迫害的受害者<br />\n好讓外國勢力不斷地比壓力支那共産黨<br />\n<br />\n大前提下大家必需<br />\n不割蓆<br />\n不指責<br />\n不被捕<br />\n不流血<br />\n不分化<br />\n大家保護大家<br />\n犯錯要包容<br />\n盡量控制自己情緒<br />\n<br />\n希望以後每一次出動<br />\n都係一場GOOD SHOW<br />\nSHOW比全世界知道<br />\n港共政府，共產黨絕對暴政<br />\nSHOW比全世界知道<br />\n我地香港人正被暴政迫害<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">GOOD SHOW</span><br />\n<br />\n以上只係小小意見<br />\n有錯請指正<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0501bdadd11290d634172c5839c768c36773e3","tid":1472062,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e57459cc2b499de353c641877963cc450b6bed","tid":1472062,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}